snippet.title: Algebra 2 – Operations with Polynomials
snippet.description:
Yay Math In Studio takes a simple look at what we can do with the operations on polynomial functions. We can add them, and multiply them, take them for walks to the store, and other fun activities like that. Don't forget to combine like terms, distribute the negative, and other important Algebra rules. Oh yeah, and YAY MATH!
